1202	// not carry the evidence required for an automated closure: a terminal
1203	// verdict event (review APPROVE with non-empty rationale, or an explicit
1204	// review-skipped / manual-close marker) AND an execution-evidence marker
1205	// (closing_commit_sha, session_id, or an execute-bead success event in the
1206	// events history).
